  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio i dovršite sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>",
  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">To be okay</span> ina maana ya kukubalika au kuruhusiwa. Kwa mfano:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Is it okay if I borrow your book?</span> – Hii ina maana ya kuuliza kama ni sawa kukopa kitabu.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Briefly</span> ina maana kitendo (kawaida, kitenzi) hutokea kwa muda mfupi au kinazungumziwa kwa maneno machache. Inatofautiana na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">brief</span>, ambayo ni kivumishi kinachoelezea kitu kilichokuwa kifupi kwa muda au urefu. Kwa mfano:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">He explained the situation briefly.</span> – Hii ina maana kitendo cha kuelezea kilikuwa kifupi.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">The meeting was brief.</span> – Hii ina maana mkutano haukuendelea kwa muda mrefu.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
